NAME

DateTime::Locale::da_GL - Locale data examples for the Danish Greenland (da-GL) locale

DESCRIPTION

This pod file contains examples of the locale data available for the Danish Greenland locale.

  tirsdag
  onsdag
  torsdag
  fredag
  lørdag
  søndag

Date Formats

Full

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = tirsdag den 5. februar 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = fredag den 22. december 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = lørdag den 15. september -10

Long

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5. februar 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22. december 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15. september -10

Medium

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5. feb. 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22. dec. 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15. sep. -10

Short

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 05.02.2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22.12.1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15.09.-10
